snippet.title: "SHE'S CRAZY" Kanye West EXPOSES Kylie Jenner (IG LIVE VIDEO)
snippet.description:
"SHE'S CRAZY" Kanye West EXPOSES Kylie Jenner (IG LIVE VIDEO)
When it comes to the Kardashian family, there is little doubt that they are one of the most fame-desiring, egotistical, and self-centered people on the planet. You can start from Kris Jenner (the matriarch of the family) go right into her “first children” via Kim, Khloe and Kourtney, and then her “next children” via Kendall and Kylie and all the evidence is there for you to see. But now, a leak of a music video from Kanye West shows rather graphically the truth about Kylie’s rise to fame. And it’s...not pretty, at all. We’ll break it down for you. Be sure to like the video and subscribe to the channel!

Click HERE To Enter The GIVEAWAY! https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCbiT0LUIbQj6CQScvWHJeKQ?sub_confirmation=1

And there you have it, everyone! A look at the various elements of the Kanye West video and how Kylie is very much someone who was “bred to be famous” and what that says about her life, her personality, and of course, her family. Do you think that Kanye went too far with this video? Do you think that he was just being honest for once and trying to expose the truth? Let us know in the comments below, be sure to subscribe and we’ll see you next time on the channel!
